021092&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2O6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=1391c537\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170514%2F20021092&h=5a44ee14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20170514/20021092</a><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英到訪美國，一口氣走訪多個共和黨票倉、傳統「紅色州分」。雖然特朗普在爭議聲中上任美國總統，但黎智英與堪薩斯州州長布朗貝克（Sam Brownback）會面時表示，選舉結果反映人民求變意願；又贊同新政府提出的減稅措施，直言美國「會再次強大起來」。"},{"pid":"356c3f78aa6af247a449b48a4f11ca3a057a4d62","tid":1156275,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90775a272b1ba7b14b3caa4d0b5c7a3b33270ac","tid":1156275,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80001ffc533fd437d70909c693161b40a24d0557","tid":1156275,"uid":204803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"侵俾人玩實會對大陸更狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大把花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6da98304cc156876ac9da42690c9ea50b12f11","tid":1156275,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"推推爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f7db12777633283061089600abb219649f8d1a","tid":1156275,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"而家只有侵爺可以救香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4431c20ce5de4b44d8e714cb5750d23f3084a98e","tid":1156275,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f7db12777633283061089600abb219649f8d1a","tid":1156275,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"而家只有侵爺可以救香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9cf125eb1801eb49628233262b365ca3568428","tid":1156275,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}